		<div id="comment_body_43593109"><p>As long as you know when to get out.  Otherwise, you'd be just like the miner - left with a lot of spare equipment of no value.  Inventory isn't free.</p></div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_43593109">
