		on Tuesday April 30, 2013 @03:07PM (<span class="ind"></span><a href="//news.slashdot.org/comments.pl?sid=3703395&amp;cid=43593477">#43593477</a>)
		<small> </small>
</span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_43593477"><p><div class="quote"><p>But bitcoin is extremely wasteful.  At least with real coins the metals are still useful.</p></div><p>Bitcoin bits are infinity reusable.  You could reuse those bits to make a picture, song, movie, spreadsheet, game, encryption key, etc.</p></div>
	</div>

