		<div class="details">
			<span class="by"><span class="byby">by </span><a href="//slashdot.org/~Nrrqshrr">Nrrqshrr</a>  <span class="uid"><a href="//slashdot.org/~Nrrqshrr">(1879148)</a></span></a></span><span class="writes" style="display:none"> writes:</span> 
			<span class="otherdetails" id="comment_otherdetails_43593153"></span>
		</div>
	</div>
	<div class="commentBody">
		<div id="comment_body_43593153">Not really a defender of Bitcoins, but:
<br>
You can get real money in four different ways:
<br> <br>
1. Have a special skill or qualification that allows you to acquire money.<br>
2. Put others to work earning you money for a profitable wage using other peoples special skills or qualifications.<br>
3. Speculate, lol.<br>
4. Steal.<br>
<br>
Only one of these is ethical.</div>
	</div>

	<div class="commentSub" id="comment_sub_43593153">

